discrepancies.issue: Field 'tAcc' is not explicitly listed in the 'Payload description' table for UBX-NAV-TIMEGPS on page 1 of the PDF manual. However, the overall message length is specified as 16 bytes. With 'valid' ending at byte offset 11 (1 byte), there are 4 bytes remaining (12, 13, 14, 15). Furthermore, the message description for UBX-NAV-TIMEGPS states it includes 'an accuracy estimate', which 'tAcc' represents.
